@18500 = ~Let us begin. <CHARNAME>, you know your host, Duke Belt, and Grand Duke Eltan, I believe?~

@18501 = ~The Flaming Fist marches with you, under Captain Corwin and Corporal Duncan. Duke Eltan sends his regrets—the ongoing crisis has called him elsewhere. Is there anything else you need before you depart?~
@18502 = ~What route will we take to Dragonspear Castle?~
@18503 = ~Can you go over the mission again?~
@18504 = ~Nothing. We are ready to march.~
@18505 = ~Is there anything else?~
@18506 = ~Then speak with Captain Corwin by the main doors. And be on your guard—the trip north will likely hold dangers beside the crusade. Tymora favor your travels, <CHARNAME>.~
